# Apply for Pro Only

When the user says **"apply for pro only"** or **"pro accounts only"**:

- Apply the change only to **professional dashboards**: doctor, nurse, pharmacy, clinic, laboratory, ambulance
- Do NOT change patient dashboard or super-admin
- Use `ProDashboardSidebar` or pro-specific components
- Old and new pro accounts get it; patients are unchanged
